ABOUT THIS SOFTWARE
This repository contains the backend server code that powers
the BurritoLauncher platform. It handles user accounts,
game uploads, chat, statistics, and other online features.

This server is intended to run ONLY on servers authorized
by Luca_nl (currently: Render.com).

